11:T8bc,{"@context":"https://schema.org","@type":"FAQPage","mainEntity":[{"@type":"Question","name":"Is there a setup fee?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"Most engagements include onboarding and strategy in month one. We quote it upfront. No surprise charges on the first invoice."}},{"@type":"Question","name":"Do you require a long-term contract?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"No. Month to month. Results should earn your business, not a contract clause."}},{"@type":"Question","name":"What affects my price?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"One-time funnel builds and ongoing optimization retainers are scoped separately based on traffic and test volume."}},{"@type":"Question","name":"Can I start with a smaller plan and upgrade?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"Yes. Many clients start on Starter and move up once momentum builds. We plan the upgrade path so you are not rebuilding from scratch."}},{"@type":"Question","name":"¿Cuánto cuesta un programa de embudos y CRO?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"Builds de embudo único con landing page, imán de leads y secuencia email parten en $5,000. Sistemas multi-oferta van de $10,000 a $30,000. Programas CRO continuos parten en $2,500 al mes para sitios con tráfico suficiente para tests A/B significativos."}},{"@type":"Question","name":"¿Necesito build de embudo y CRO al mismo tiempo?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"No siempre. Si ya tienes un embudo con tráfico, podemos empezar con auditoría CRO y testing. Si lanzas desde cero, construimos el sistema y optimizamos desde el día uno."}},{"@type":"Question","name":"¿Cuánto tarda ver lift en conversión?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"Los builds de embudo lanzan en 4 a 8 semanas. Tests A/B suelen alcanzar significancia estadística en 2 a 4 semanas según tráfico. La mayoría de clientes ve lift medible en los primeros 60 a 90 días."}},{"@type":"Question","name":"¿Cuánto tráfico necesito para A/B testing?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"Recomendamos al menos 1,000 sesiones mensuales en páginas testeadas. Embudos con menos tráfico aún se benefician de fixes UX basados en auditoría e insights de heatmaps."}}]}6:[[["$","script","0",{"type":"application/ld+json","dangerouslySetInnerHTML":{"__html":"{\"@context\":\"https://schema.org\",\"@type\":\"Organization\",\"name\":\"KINEXIS Digital\",\"url\":\"https://www.kinexisdigital.com\",\"logo\":\"https://www.kinexisdigital.com/logo.png\",\"description\":\"Digital marketing agency specializing in SEO, paid media, web design, CRO, and analytics for local businesses, SaaS companies, and enterprise organizations.\",\"sameAs\":[\"https://www.linkedin.com/company/kinexisdigital\"],\"contactPoint\":{\"@type\":\"ContactPoint\",\"contactType\":\"sales\",\"availableLanguage\":[\"English\",\"Spanish\",\"French\",\"German\"]}}"}}],["$","script","1",{"type":"application/ld+json","dangerouslySetInnerHTML":{"__html":"{\"@context\":\"https://schema.org\",\"@type\":\"Service\",\"name\":\"Funnels & Conversion Rate Optimization Pricing\",\"description\":\"Transparent funnels & conversion rate optimization pricing with clear tiers and deliverables. No hidden fees. No vague retainers.\",\"provider\":{\"@type\":\"Organization\",\"name\":\"KINEXIS Digital\",\"url\":\"https://www.kinexisdigital.com\"},\"url\":\"https://www.kinexisdigital.com/es/pricing/funnels\",\"areaServed\":\"Worldwide\"}"}}],["$","script","2",{"type":"application/ld+json","dangerouslySetInnerHTML":{"__html":"$11"}}],"$L12"],"$L13"]
