13:["$","$L14",null,{"slug":"funnels","locale":"es","content":{"metaTitle":"Funnels & Conversion Rate Optimization Pricing | Transparent Plans | KINEXIS Digital","metaDescription":"Transparent funnels & conversion rate optimization pricing with clear tiers and deliverables. No hidden fees. No vague retainers.","hero":{"label":"Funnels & Conversion Rate Optimization Pricing","line1":"Funnels & Conversion Rate Optimization Pricing","line2":"without the guesswork.","subtitle":"Fixed scope at each tier. You see what is included before you sign anything."},"answerBlock":"Traffic without a system is wasted, and a funnel without optimization stops compounding. Most businesses have ads, a website, and maybe an email list, but no connected path from first click to booked call, and no testing program to find what's actually breaking conversion. One-time funnel builds and ongoing optimization retainers are scoped separately based on traffic and test volume.","tiers":[{"name":"Starter","range":"$$3,000","description":"Single funnel build with landing page, 5-email nurture sequence, and conversion tracking setup.","bestFor":"Single funnel build with landing page, 5-email nurture sequence, and conversion tracking setup."},{"name":"Growth","range":"$$6,500/mo","description":"Full funnel system with automation, monthly A/B testing, and ongoing CRO on key conversion pages.","bestFor":"Full funnel system with automation, monthly A/B testing, and ongoing CRO on key conversion pages."},{"name":"Scale","range":"$$12,000+/mo","description":"Multi-funnel revenue system with advanced segmentation, personalization, and continuous experimentation.","bestFor":"Multi-funnel revenue system with advanced segmentation, personalization, and continuous experimentation."}],"tiersSection":{"title":"Investment guidance","subtitle":"Pricing based on funnel complexity, traffic volume, and test scope.","note":"One-time funnel builds and ongoing optimization retainers are scoped separately based on traffic and test volume."},"included":["Funnel Audit & Architecture","Landing Page Design & Build","Lead Magnets & Nurture Automation","A/B & Multivariate Testing","UX Research & Heatmap Analysis","End-to-End Tracking & Reporting"],"includedSection":{"title":"What's included","subtitle":"Funnel design, build, automation, and ongoing conversion rate optimization in one program.","items":[{"title":"Funnel Audit & Architecture","description":"Full buyer journey map with conversion data at every stage, gap identification, and offer positioning."},{"title":"Landing Page Design & Build","description":"CRO-optimized landing pages built for specific traffic sources with conversion-focused copy and structure."},{"title":"Lead Magnets & Nurture Automation","description":"High-value capture assets plus multi-step email and SMS sequences that move leads toward booking."},{"title":"A/B & Multivariate Testing","description":"Hypothesis-driven experiments on headlines, CTAs, forms, and layouts with statistical significance gates."},{"title":"UX Research & Heatmap Analysis","description":"Session recordings, heatmaps, and user behavior analysis to prioritize the highest-impact tests."},{"title":"End-to-End Tracking & Reporting","description":"Conversion tracking at every funnel stage plus monthly test results, winners, and rollout recommendations."}]},"comparison":{"title":"Investment guidance","subtitle":"Pricing based on funnel complexity, traffic volume, and test scope.","layout":"progression","columns":[{"header":"Starter","highlight":false},{"header":"Growth","highlight":true},{"header":"Scale","highlight":false}],"rows":[{"label":"Funnel Audit & Architecture","values":["Core","Standard","Advanced"]},{"label":"Landing Page Design & Build","values":["Core","Standard","Advanced"]},{"label":"Lead Magnets & Nurture Automation","values":["Core","Standard","Advanced"]},{"label":"A/B & Multivariate Testing","values":["Core","Standard","Advanced"]},{"label":"Best for","values":["Single funnel build with landing page, 5-email nurture sequence, and conversion tracking setup.","Full funnel system with automation, monthly A/B testing, and ongoing CRO on key conversion pages.","Multi-funnel revenue system with advanced segmentation, personalization, and continuous experimentation."]},{"label":"Starting investment","values":["$$3,000","$$6,500/mo","$$12,000+/mo"]}]},"faqs":[{"question":"Is there a setup fee?","answer":"Most engagements include onboarding and strategy in month one. We quote it upfront. No surprise charges on the first invoice."},{"question":"Do you require a long-term contract?","answer":"No. Month to month. Results should earn your business, not a contract clause."},{"question":"What affects my price?","answer":"One-time funnel builds and ongoing optimization retainers are scoped separately based on traffic and test volume."},{"question":"Can I start with a smaller plan and upgrade?","answer":"Yes. Many clients start on Starter and move up once momentum builds. We plan the upgrade path so you are not rebuilding from scratch."},{"question":"¿Cuánto cuesta un programa de embudos y CRO?","answer":"Builds de embudo único con landing page, imán de leads y secuencia email parten en $5,000. Sistemas multi-oferta van de $10,000 a $30,000. Programas CRO continuos parten en $2,500 al mes para sitios con tráfico suficiente para tests A/B significativos."},{"question":"¿Necesito build de embudo y CRO al mismo tiempo?","answer":"No siempre. Si ya tienes un embudo con tráfico, podemos empezar con auditoría CRO y testing. Si lanzas desde cero, construimos el sistema y optimizamos desde el día uno."},{"question":"¿Cuánto tarda ver lift en conversión?","answer":"Los builds de embudo lanzan en 4 a 8 semanas. Tests A/B suelen alcanzar significancia estadística en 2 a 4 semanas según tráfico. La mayoría de clientes ve lift medible en los primeros 60 a 90 días."},{"question":"¿Cuánto tráfico necesito para A/B testing?","answer":"Recomendamos al menos 1,000 sesiones mensuales en páginas testeadas. Embudos con menos tráfico aún se benefician de fixes UX basados en auditoría e insights de heatmaps."}],"ctaHeadline":"Want a quote for funnels & conversion rate optimization?","ctaSubtitle":"Tell us your goals, market, and scope.|We will recommend the right tier and show you what the first 90 days look like.","ctaLabel":"Get Funnels & Conversion Rate Optimization Pricing"},"serviceHref":"/services/funnels","serviceLabel":"Funnels & Conversion Rate Optimization","breadcrumbs":[{"name":"Home","url":"/"},{"name":"Services","url":"/services"},{"name":"Funnels & Conversion Rate Optimization","url":"/services/funnels"},{"name":"Funnels & Conversion Rate Optimization Pricing"}]}]
